# Custom Rules & Style Guidelines

## Badges & Status Colors
- **Rule**: Never use hardcoded colors (like `color="primary"`) for status badges or status indicator components.
- **Helper**: Always resolve the status color dynamically using the shared `commonUtil.getStatusColor(statusId)` helper from `@common`.
- **Example**:
  ```html
  <ion-badge :color="commonUtil.getStatusColor(order.statusId)">
    {{ order.status }}
  </ion-badge>
  ```
